: \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I mean third time's a charm, that's what they say.\", \"from\": 2378, \"to\": 2428, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am excited to go to Paris and these Games this time around.\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2490, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2451, \"end\": 2456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.65189913177294e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am just pumped up.\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2511, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just want to keep going out there, leave a mark in this sport, and create a legacy that people will look up to and be inspired by.\", \"from\": 2513, \"to\": 2646, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So yeah, I gotta keep going until the wheels fall off, as they say.\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2714, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think for me, I never liked to put a time limit or expiration on how many Olympics I can do.\", \"from\": 2716, \"to\": 2811, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think my goal and objective is to make it to at least 2028 LA because I feel like that would be a full-circle moment for me.\", \"from\": 2812, \"to\": 2938, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's where I kind of started my career.\\\"\", \"from\": 2939, \"to\": 2981, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Canada are yet to win a medalat the Paris Olympics, with the men's 200m final scheduled to take place on Thursday.\", \"from\": 2983, \"to\": 3097, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2983, \"end\": 2989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.8870538527593115, \"rank\": 0.1271076667175369, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/reso